No...doubt...nooo!! Mashhallah...👏
*Aey Farishto Woh*
*Sultane Me'raj Hen*
*Tum Jo Dekhoge*
*Hairaan Ho Jaaoge*
*ZULF TAFSEERE*
*Wal Lail Ban Jayegi*
*Chahera Qu'ran*
*Saara Nazar Aayega*
*Chahera Nazar Aayega..*
*Chahera Nazar Aayega..*
.....Actually I can't understand this song...but I don't know y...ye song dil ko 6uu gaya...pata nahi kyu ye lines sunkar mere rongte khade ho gaye...yhh my religion is hindu..jo sirf mere insaan hone ka 'title' hen..Ki han me hindu dharm se bilong karti hun😑...ye song mene thodi der pehle hi suna...mene namaz padhate Hue dekha he...but movies me yah live Masjid ki khidkiyo se...but aaj jab chal rahi thi...suddenly mene aage Masjid dekhi..or bahar sab namaz padh rahe the...n this second time to happened with me...rongte khade ho gaye...muh se nikla Alhamdulillah..
I don't know y...jo song vali feeling thi...vesi hi feelings..usse bhi badhkar aayi...ki manoo dharm k jativad se hat kar...Allah bhagvan....zarur hen...yakinan...
sare bhaiyo baheno ko Ramzaan mubarak.
